=== YOUR ASSIGNED PROBLEM ===
UUID: ${p.uuid}
TITLE: ${p.title}
DOMAIN (for <domain>_service.py / test_<domain>.py): ${p.domain}
PROBLEM STATEMENT (put this in §1 and return it verbatim): ${p.problemStatement}

